                "invention-title": [
                    "Hearth type ammonia decomposition reactor and system",
                    "一种炉膛式氨分解反应器及系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hearth type ammonia decomposition reactor and system. The hearth type ammonia decomposition reactor comprises a furnace body, an ammonia gas pipeline, a plurality of ammonia decomposition pipelines, an exhaust pipeline, an air pipeline and a plurality of combustors, the furnace body comprises an annular distribution section and a combustion hearth, the combustion hearth is sleeved with the annular distribution section, the annular distribution section is communicated with the combustion hearth, the air pipeline is communicated with the annular distribution section, and the ammonia gas pipeline is communicated with the furnace body; one end of each ammonia decomposition pipeline is communicated with the ammonia gas pipeline, the other end of each ammonia decomposition pipeline extends into the combustion hearth in the direction close to the combustion hearth and penetrates through the bottom of the combustion hearth, and the other end of each ammonia decomposition pipeline is communicated with the exhaust pipeline; the exhaust pipeline is provided with a plurality of branches and is communicated with a combustor in the combustion hearth through the branches. According to the hearth type ammonia decomposition reactor, the energy of gas in the ammonia decomposition and heating combustion process is fully utilized, the overall energy utilization rate is increased, the energy consumption of the reactor is reduced, and the overall integration level is high."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本申请公开了一种炉膛式氨分解反应器及系统，包括炉体、氨气管道、多个氨分解管道、排气管道、空气管道和多个燃烧器；炉体包括环形分布区间和燃烧炉膛，环形分布区间套设在燃烧炉膛外部并且和燃烧炉膛相连通，空气管道与环形分布区间连通，氨气管道与炉体相通；多个氨分解管道的一端与氨气管道连通，另一端朝向靠近燃烧炉膛的方向延伸进入燃烧炉膛内部并且穿过燃烧炉膛的底部，多个氨分解管道的另一端与排气管道连通；排气管道上开设有多个支路并通过多个支路与燃烧炉膛内的燃烧器连通。该炉膛式氨分解反应器充分利用了氨气分解和加热燃烧过程中气体自身的能量，提高了整体的能量利用率，减少了反应器的能量消耗，且整体集成度高。"
                }
